item.title: Data Interlinked
The Trouble with Triples
item.description: In the Star Trek episode “The Trouble with Tribbles” the crew of the starship Enterprise encounters creatures called Tribbles. They are cute, simple creatures of mysterious origin that seem harmless at first but when they multiply the pose a big problem for the ship and the crew. Tribbles Tribbles © 1967 Paramount Pictures Representing and reasoning with knowledge have surprisingly similar problems. A single fact on its own is a relatively straightforward affair.
